At the server side:
COMPILE USING :: sudo gcc -Wall -o ssl-server ssl_server.c -lssl -lcrypto
run ::::::::::::  "./server cert.pem key.pem port"

At the client side:
compile using ::sudo gcc -Wall -o ssl-client ssl_client.c -lssl -lcrypto
run           ::"./client hostname port"


if you want to close client put input of X =-1 ,client will close








